t-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">Criciuma - Figueirense</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"border:1px solid #dddddd;\">\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">GIAO H\u1eeeU CLB 2018</span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"border:1px solid #dddddd;\">\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: center;\">05/07 18:30</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">Schalke 04 - Southampton</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"border:1px solid #dddddd;\">\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: center;\">05/07 23:00</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">Austria Vienna - Shakhtar Donetsk</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"border:1px solid #dddddd;\">\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: center;\">05/07 23:30</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">Furstenwalde - Union Berlin</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"border:1px solid #dddddd;\">\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n            <div>05/07 23:30</div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">FK  \t\tRostov - Trencin</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"910","checkdouble":"190390"},{"date":"07:11 05/07","title":"Kompany: B\u1ec9 s\u1ee3 g\u00ec c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao Brazil?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/kompany-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-bi-vs-brazil.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Vincent Kompany ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Brazil. Trung v\u1ec7 k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t ng\u1ee7 khi ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi Neymar c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Brazil.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t ng\u1ee7 v\u00ec Brazil</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong khi Brazil v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Mexico 2-0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, \u0110T B\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd th\u1ee9 4 c\u1ee7a Nacer Chadli \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 3-2. Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3, HLV Roberto Martinez tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 khi ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Brazil t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, trung v\u1ec7 Vincent Kompany ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Brazil c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u201cC\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng Brazil l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t trong World Cup 2018\u201d, anh n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi khen nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ecd. Kh\u00f4ng ai trong \u0110T B\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t ng\u1ee7 v\u00e0 ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd thua Brazil.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Vincent Kompany ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Brazil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Vincent Kompany ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Brazil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Vincent-Kompany-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-Bi-vs-Brazil-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">B\u1ec9 nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 3-2</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cH\u1ecd ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 nh\u1eefng pha 1 vs 1. H\u1ecd lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1edf ra m\u1ecdi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd xem x\u00e9t m\u1ecdi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. N\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3, n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho nhau, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng theo quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kompany cua Bi\" title=\"Kompany cua Bi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/kompany-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-bi-vs-brazil.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kompany ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Brazil \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o HLV Martinez</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Roberto Martinez, B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng. C\u1ef1u HLV Everton \u01b0a th\u00edch s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-4-3 \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. V\u00e0 Kompany kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng d\u00f9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u1ed7i trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thi tri\u1ec3n m\u1ed9t phong c\u00e1ch h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d, Kompany n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p kh\u00e1c khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Brazil.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T B\u1ec9 tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-bi-32-nhat-ban-421-190297.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hazard-tiet-lo-su-khac-biet-cua-dt-bi-421-190265.html\">Hazard ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/don-quyet-dinh-tieu-diet-samurai-xanh-cua-bi-su-dong-gop-tinh-te-cua-lukaku-421-190257.html\">\u0110\u00f2n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t Samurai xanh c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9: S\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p tinh t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Lukaku</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-bi-32-nhat-ban-quy-do-no-samurai-loi-cam-on-421-190243.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf n\u1ee3 Samurai l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-nguoc-dong-kho-tin-cua-bi-truoc-nhat-ban-421-190239.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau m\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kh\u00f3 tin c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"909","checkdouble":"190392"},{"date":"07:34 05/07","title":"Mourinho b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00e0i\u2026 \u201c\u0111\u00f3ng k\u1ecbch\u201d c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/mourinho-phat-bieu-ve-dt-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh \u0111ang d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u x\u1ea5u x\u00ed t\u1ea1i Moscow</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018. C\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2 do c\u00f4ng Harry Kane t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n nh\u01b0ng Tam s\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3. T\u1edbi ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd th\u1ee9 3, trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 cho Colombia \u0111\u01b0a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau 30 ph\u00fat \u0111\u00e1 th\u00eam kh\u00f4ng ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng b\u1ea1i, hai \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m. \u1ede \u0111\u00e2y, \u0110T anh t\u1ecf ra chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c h\u01a1n trong c\u00e1c c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh \u0111ang d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh \u0111ang d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/mourinho-phat-bieu-ve-dt-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n c\u00e3i v\u00e3 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf tr\u1eadn Anh vs Colombia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh x\u1ea5u x\u00ed. Li\u00ean t\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i, c\u00e3i v\u00e3 c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eaft v\u1ee5n m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i. T\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 8 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh r\u00fat ra v\u1edbi 6 cho Colombia, 2 cho Anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Anh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh khi\u1ebfn cho HLV Jose Mourinho c\u1ee7a Man United ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00edch danh Harry Maguire, t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Leicester City c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0103n v\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho noi ve DT Duc sau tran thua soc\" title=\"Mourinho n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/MU-muon-mua-Leonardo-Bonucci-voi-gia-37-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1eadt. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n \u0111\u00f3ng k\u1ecbch th\u00e1i qu\u00e1 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7\u201d, Mourinho n\u00f3i tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1edd b\u00e1o c\u1ee7a Nga. \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi th\u1ea5y bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c trung v\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 Harry Maguire.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ea5t trung th\u1ef1c, nh\u01b0ng tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i ng\u00e3 v\u1edd trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2i tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i d\u00f9ng VAR. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u0103n v\u1ea1, nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n ng\u00e3 v\u1edd v\u00e0 g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u00ean tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ea5t \u0111i ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Anh vs Colombia tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-chien-thang-cua-anh-truoc-colombia-421-190371.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/tai-sao-vardy-khong-duoc-da-luan-luu-truoc-colombia-469-190368.html\">T\u1ea1i sao Vardy kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/falcao-cay-cu-anh-chien-thang-vi-trong-tai-421-190363.html\">Falcao cay c\u00fa: Anh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00ec tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lingard-anh-da-cho-doi-ngay-nay-rat-lau-roi-421-190364.html\">Lingard: Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i ng\u00e0y n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u r\u1ed3i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-colombia-tu-hao-du-bai-tran-truoc-anh-421-190358.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o d\u00f9 b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"908","checkdouble":"190394"},{"date":"07:21 05/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 05/07: MU v\u00e0 Chelsea n\u1ed5 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d c\u00f9ng l\u00fac","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-0507-mu-va-chelsea-no-bom-tan-cung-luc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 05/07.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU v\u00e0 Chelsea n\u1ed5 &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; c\u00f9ng l\u00fac</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 0507 MU v\u00e0 Chelsea n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 0507 MU v\u00e0 Chelsea n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/chelsea-chi-ban-willian-cho-mu-voi-mot-dieu-kien.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n Willian c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Sport Mediaset, MU v\u00e0 Chelsea nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u1edbn v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 7. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Chelsea chi 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Gonzalo Higuain th\u00ec M.U b\u1ecf ra 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Willian.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Wenger b\u1ecb ch\u00e2m bi\u1ebfm sau ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n s\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 Jordan Pickford</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsene Wenger ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jordan Pickford, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Everton l\u00e0 m\u1eaft x\u00edch y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Colombia. C\u1ef1u HLV Arsenal \u0111ang g\u1eb7p r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i l\u1edbn v\u1edbi nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Sao sa c\u01a1 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea7u c\u1ee9u Liverpool</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xherdan Shaqiri mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League thay v\u00ec xu\u1ed1ng gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh c\u00f9ng Stoke City. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y thay cho l\u1eddi nh\u1eafc v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang theo \u0111u\u1ed5i anh nh\u01b0 Liverpool.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/shaqiri-muon-o-lai-premier-league-172-190387.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/shaqiri-muon-o-lai-premier-league.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/shaqiri-muon-o-lai-premier-league-172-190387.html\">Sao sa c\u01a1 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea7u c\u1ee9u Liverpool</span><br>\r\nXherdan Shaqiri mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League thay v\u00ec xu\u1ed1ng gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh c\u00f9ng Stoke City. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y thay cho l\u1eddi nh\u1eafc v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang theo \u0111u\u1ed5i anh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110T Anh c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Vardy</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jamie Vardy d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e1ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0110T Anh cung c\u1ea5p.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t HLV b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i sau World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Oscar Ramirez bi Costa Rica sa thai\" title=\"Oscar Ramirez b\u1ecb Costa Rica sa th\u1ea3i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/them-mot-hlv-bi-sa-thai-sau-world-cup-2018.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Oscar Ramirez b\u1ecb Costa Rica sa th\u1ea3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Costa Rica sa th\u1ea3i HLV Oscar Ramirez \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Costa Rica, \u00f4ng Fedefutbol Rodolfo Villalobos x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/them-mot-hlv-bi-sa-thai-sau-world-cup-2018-421-190383.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/them-mot-hlv-bi-sa-thai-sau-world-cup-2018.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/them-mot-hlv-bi-sa-thai-sau-world-cup-2018-421-190383.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t HLV b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i sau World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nCosta Rica sa th\u1ea3i HLV Oscar Ramirez \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Costa Rica, \u00f4ng Fedefutbol Rodolfo Villalobos x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 \u0110T \u00dd khuy\u00ean Neymar ng\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3ng k\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng pha &ldquo;\u0103n v\u1ea1&rdquo; t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 \u0110T \u00dd, Claudio Gentile \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khuy\u00ean ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i d\u1eebng vi\u1ec7c di\u1ec5n k\u1ecbch.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea h\u1ecfi mua Mateo Kovacic</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Bernabeu \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Everton chi 24 tri\u1ec7u euro mua sao Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mina ghi ban cho Colombia\" title=\"Mina ghi ban cho Colombia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-ngay-47-MU-quan-tam-sao-tuyen-Croatia-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Everton mu\u1ed1n mua Mina&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Liverpool Echo, Everton s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 24 tri\u1ec7u euro mua trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1eeba c\u00f3 k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Colombia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kante \u01b0u ti\u00ean PSG h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mirror, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p r\u1eddi Chelsea ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kante \u01b0u ti\u00ean chuy\u1ec3n v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1 cho PSG thay v\u00ec kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"907","checkdouble":"190395"},{"date":"08:23 05/07","title":"C\u1ef1u HLV Anh b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/cuu-hlv-anh-bat-ngo-ung-ho-thuy-dien-chien-thang.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ef1c ra th\u00ec c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i th\u00f4i khi Sven-Goran Eriksson v\u1ed1n l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng d\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1eafc \u00c2u n\u00e0y v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean c\u1ed5 v\u0169 cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 trong tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y kia.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">L\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 v\u00e0 Colombia theo nh\u1eefng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh h\u1eb9n g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, v\u1edbi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Tam S\u01b0 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 28 n\u0103m.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Erikson n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Erikson n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/cuu-hlv-anh-bat-ngo-ung-ho-thuy-dien-chien-thang.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Erikson n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Andreas Granqvist kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/granqvist-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-thuy-dien-vs-anh-421-190391.html\" target=\"_blank\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh</span>, HLV Sven-Goran Eriksson c\u0169ng t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00e0 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Tam S\u01b0 nh\u1eefng n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1eadp ni\u00ean 2000:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i tin m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ebd d\u00e0nh cho Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed Anh c\u00f2n ghi n\u1ed5i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra khi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup r\u1ed3i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 lo\u1ea1i \u00dd tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ebfn Nga v\u1edbi m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch, trong khi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ghi b\u00e0n t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t. Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u01b0 Harry Kane, nh\u01b0ng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mang s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 Eriksson n\u00f3i, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu cho Anh khi \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng thua trong hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp (2002 v\u00e0 2006, khi ch\u00ednh Eriksson d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Tam S\u01b0). \u0110\u1ed9i th\u1eafng trong c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Croatia ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-ay-la-zlatan-nhung-chung-ta-la-thuy-dien-421-188871.html\">Anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 Zlatan, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta l\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-thuy-dien-vs-thuy-si-nguoi-hung-emil-forsberg-421-190326.html\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n-kh\u00f4ng-Ibra ti\u1ebfn xa \u1edf World Cup: H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh phi th\u01b0\u1eddng vi\u1ebft b\u1edfi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"906","checkdouble":"190396"},{"date":"08:45 05/07","title":"K\u1ef3 World Cup c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta ngh\u0129","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/2/ky-world-cup-cua-tay-ban-nha-khong-te-nhu-nguoi-ta-nghi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u HLV Vicente Del Bosque kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch ng\u1eafn ng\u1ee7i tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, T\u00e2y Ban Nha th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n m\u1ea1o b\u1ebf t\u1eafc v\u00e0 b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf c\u1ea3 ba tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf World Cup 2018. Iran v\u00e0 Maroc kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u00ec ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn La Roja ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 ngay v\u00f2ng 1/8 v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Del Bosque n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a TBN \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Del Bosque n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a TBN \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/ky-world-cup-cua-tay-ban-nha-khong-te-nhu-nguoi-ta-nghi.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Del Bosque n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a TBN \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 t\u1eeb d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi \u0111\u00e2y d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 h\u1eadu qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ed1c n\u1ed5i sa th\u1ea3i HLV Julen Lopetegui ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Vicente Del Bosque l\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u0110TQG t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2010 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u1edf hai k\u1ef3 Euro li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. T\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean qu\u00e1 kh\u1eaft khe v\u00e0 t\u00e0n nh\u1eabn v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u1eeb ng\u1eef n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang ta v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c nh\u01b0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nga. Quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u00fat ra v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp thu cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Fernando Hierro kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch khi ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao l\u00e2u, trong khi t\u00f4i th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang ta n\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tbn-bi-loai-khoi-world-cup-2018-ngay-la-roja-mac-ket-giua-hai-the-he-421-190135.html\">TBN b\u1eadt b\u00e3i World Cup 2018: Ng\u00e0y La Roja m\u1eafc k\u1eb9t gi\u1eefa hai th\u1ebf h\u1ec7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-tbn-vs-nga-toi-dep-khong-den-voi-nguoi-cho-doi-421-190136.html\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00fai \u0111\u1ea7u ra \u0111i: T\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i n\u00f3</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tay-ban-nha-bi-loai-khoi-world-cup-hay-de-tikitaka-vao-tu-kinh-421-190138.html\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018: H\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 tiki-taka v\u00e0o t\u1ee7 k\u00ednh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/that-bai-cua-dt-tay-ban-nha-thoi-ky-den-toi-da-quay-tro-lai-466-190370.html\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha: Th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 \u0111en t\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"905","checkdouble":"190397"},{"date":"21:58 04/07","title":"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u2018m\u00e0i s\u1eafc\u2019 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm L\u00e0o","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/u19-viet-nam-mai-sac-hang-cong-quyet-thang-dam-lao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>R\u00fat kinh nghi\u1ec7m t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U18 cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u00ec thua k\u00e9m hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1ea1i, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang t\u00edch c\u1ef1c ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>\u00a0U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u00edch c\u1ef1c luy\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, h\u1ecd chia \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi U19 Th\u00e1i Lan tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm Philippines 5-0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. B\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng l\u00e0 trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 u\u1ed1n n\u1eafn t\u1eebng chi ti\u1ebft nh\u1ecf cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\" U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u00e0i s\u1eafc h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm L\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\" U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u00e0i s\u1eafc h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm L\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/u19-viet-nam-06-2125.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam mi\u1ec7t m\u00e0i luy\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u 4/7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p U19 L\u00e0o, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia l\u00e0m 2 nh\u00f3m, m\u1ed9t nh\u00f3m h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c v\u00e0 nh\u00f3m c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, t\u1eadp b\u00e0i 4 ch\u1ed1ng 4. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u00e9t n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c\u00a0HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n\u00a0d\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian r\u00e8n gi\u0169a kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u00f3m c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0 tuy\u1ebfn 2 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam quy\u1ebft ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng Tu\u1ea5n \u2018con\u2019 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Philippines. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Philippines c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n. Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 Philippines c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t. Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 mang l\u1ea1i cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5-0 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay\u201d, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00f3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi U19 L\u00e0o v\u00e0o l\u00fac 15h30 ng\u00e0y mai 5/7. Tr\u00ean BXH b\u1ea3ng A l\u00fac n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i. U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai v\u1edbi 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 Th\u00e1i Lan nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng/thua t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. V\u00ec v\u1eady, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean BXH.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"904","checkdouble":"190381"},{"date":"22:36 04/07","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Brazil ch\u1ec9 ra b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1ea5t cho Neymar","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/huyen-thoai-brazil-chi-ra-ben-do-ly-tuong-nhat-cho-neymar.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi t\u1edd  Sport Bild, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Brazil Rivaldo cho r\u1eb1ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar n\u00ean chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</h2><h2>\"Neymar c\u1ea7n t\u1edbi Real \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c QBV\"</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng tin CLB Real Madrid s\u1ebd b\u1ecf ra 310 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Neymar. Tuy nhi\u00ean ph\u00eda Real \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u00e1c b\u1ecf tin \u0111\u1ed3n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Brazil ch\u1ec9 ra b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1ea5t cho Neymar h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Brazil ch\u1ec9 ra b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1ea5t cho Neymar h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/toa-sang-ruc-ro-truoc-mexico-nguoi-hung-neymar-noi-gi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Rivaldo cho r\u1eb1ng Neymar n\u00ean chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t CLB l\u1edbn h\u01a1n nh\u01b0 Real Madrid</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean theo quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Rivaldo, ng\u00f4i sao l\u1eebng danh m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Brazil th\u00ec \u2018ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n em\u2019 n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n cao qu\u00fd nh\u01b0 Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2002 cho bi\u1ebft:\u00a0 \u201cTheo t\u00f4i, Neymar r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng khi ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i PSG. N\u1ebfu Neymar mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea1m tay v\u00e0o danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00f2 t\u00e1 HLV Thomas Tuchel t\u1ea1i PSG. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf, Neymar c\u1ea7n gia nh\u1eadp nh\u1eefng n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u01a1n nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i TBN v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do cho vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Real l\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Neymar gia nh\u1eadp PSG t\u1eeb Barcelona v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 220 tri\u1ec7u euro trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2017. Thgi\u00fa\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y gi\u00fap anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh. Tuy nhi\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn PSG \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea5m chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00f4m th\u1ee9 Ba v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, L\u0110B\u0110 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u UEFA c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o vi\u1ec7c xem x\u00e9t v\u00e0 l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng t\u1ecf vi\u1ec7c CLB PSG vi ph\u1ea1m lu\u1eadt c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2017, xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p b\u1ecf ra qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu Neymar.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cuu-danh-thu-dt-y-khuyen-neymar-ngung-dong-kich-tai-world-cup-2018-421-190380.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/cuu-danh-thu-dt-y-khuyen-neymar-ngung-dong-kich-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cuu-danh-thu-dt-y-khuyen-neymar-ngung-dong-kich-tai-world-cup-2018-421-190380.html\">C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 \u0110T \u00dd khuy\u00ean Neymar ng\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3ng k\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng pha \u2018\u0103n v\u1ea1\u2019 t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 \u0110T \u00dd, Claudio Gentile \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean cho ng\u00f4i sao...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-37-real-madrid-phu-nhan-lien-he-voi-neymar-184-190300.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/8/4/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-37-real-madrid-phu-nhan-lien-he-voi-neymar.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-37-real-madrid-phu-nhan-lien-he-voi-neymar-184-190300.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 3/7: Real Madrid ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Neymar</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 3/7.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-bi-thua-nhan-neymar-don-gian-khong-the-can-421-190309.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/sao-bi-thua-nhan-neymar-don-gian-khong-the-can.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-bi-thua-nhan-neymar-don-gian-khong-the-can-421-190309.html\">Sao B\u1ec9 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Neymar \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Thomas Meunier chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u00f4i sao \u1edf Paris Saint-Germain trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Brazil vs B\u1ec9 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"903","checkdouble":"190382"},{"date":"05:41 05/07","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t HLV b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i sau World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/them-mot-hlv-bi-sa-thai-sau-world-cup-2018.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Xherdan Shaqiri mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League thay v\u00ec xu\u1ed1ng gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh c\u00f9ng Stoke City. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y thay cho l\u1eddi nh\u1eafc v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang theo \u0111u\u1ed5i anh nh\u01b0 Liverpool hay Tottenham.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Shaqiri c\u00f9ng Stoke xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, Stoke City ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 19 tr\u00ean BXH Premier League. Sau 38 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, 12 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a trong khi \u0111\u00e3 thua t\u1edbi 19. Qua \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh The Potters ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i xu\u1ed1ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc cho ng\u00f4i sao Xherdan Shaqiri. Chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch 2017/18 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129. Anh \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, 7 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Stoke. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 35 b\u00e0n, t\u00ednh ra Shaqiri \u0111\u00e3 tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o 43% s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Shaqiri mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League thay v\u00ec xu\u1ed1ng gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Shaqiri mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League thay v\u00ec xu\u1ed1ng gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/shaqiri-muon-o-lai-premier-league.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Xherdan Shaqiri mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Xherdan Shaqiri mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 Liverpool hay Tottenham \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft. \u201cT\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec. T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i s\u1ebd s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft\u201d, Shaqiri n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y b\u1edfi t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0110TQG v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 CLB quan t\u00e2m c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. \u0110\u00f4i khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o t\u00f4i. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i \u1edf s\u00e2n kh\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady d\u00f9 trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd bi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Shaqiri c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Th\u1ee5y S\u0129. Anh \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n, 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i b\u1edfi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-muon-gay-soc-voi-chu-lun-de-thuong-172-187932.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/24/liverpool-muon-gay-soc-voi-chu-lun-de-thuong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-muon-gay-soc-voi-chu-lun-de-thuong-172-187932.html\">Liverpool mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi \u201cch\u00fa l\u00f9n\u201d d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span><br>\r\n<span>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Xherdan Shaqiri c\u1ee7a Stoke City \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng bi\u00ean, The Kop s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 12 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"902","checkdouble":"190383"},{"date":"06:01 05/07","title":"\u0110T Anh c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Vardy","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/dt-anh-cap-nhat-tinh-hinh-chan-thuong-cua-vardy.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jamie Vardy d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e1ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0110T Anh cung c\u1ea5p. HLV Southgate c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Leicester.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vardy d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Vardy ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u1edf ph\u00fat 88 thay Sterling. Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Leicester ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a anh nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n khi\u1ebfn Colombia g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jamie Vardy d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jamie Vardy d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/Jamie-Vardy-dinh-chan-thuong-truoc-tran-gap-Thuy-Dien-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Vardy d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e1ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Colombia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 11m, NHM Anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi Vardy kh\u00f4ng b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t. B\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf ch\u1ed7 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Leicester c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 11m, anh \u0111\u00e3 s\u00fat th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 6 trong 7 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c giao tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Southgate sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/tai-sao-vardy-khong-duoc-da-luan-luu-truoc-colombia-469-190368.html\" target=\"_blank\">Vardy kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 11m cho \u0110T Anh</span>, theo \u0111\u00f3 anh d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecdn ra 5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 penalty t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecdn Vardy b\u1edfi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e1ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 th\u1ee9 2, vi\u1ec7c\u00a0kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i g\u1ea1t Vardy kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 11m\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Vardy kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jamie Vardy d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e1ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0110T Anh cung c\u1ea5p.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Vardy dinh chan thuong hang\" title=\"Vardy d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e1ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/dt-anh-cap-nhat-tinh-hinh-chan-thuong-cua-vardy.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Vardy d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e1ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cVardy g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf h\u00e1ng trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Colombia \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c ki\u1ec3m tra t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 xem x\u00e9t m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn Vardy kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng khi Vardy kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"901","checkdouble":"190385"},{"date":"06:15 05/07","title":"Willian ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca quan t\u00e2m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/11/willian-chinh-thuc-len-tieng-truoc-tin-don-duoc-barca-quan-tam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Willian ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Barca l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi Camp Nou.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca quan t\u00e2m Willian</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, HLV Ernesto Valverde \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. Vi\u1ec7c Antoine Griezmann g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Atletico bu\u1ed9c Barca ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eafm m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca v\u00e0 MU quan t\u00e2m Willian ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca v\u00e0 MU quan t\u00e2m Willian ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Duoc-Barca-va-MU-quan-tam-Willian-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Willian\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edd b\u00e1o c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-khong-ban-willian-cho-barca-172-189958.html\" target=\"_blank\">Barca quan t\u00e2m Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span>. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed Philippe Coutinho v\u00e0 Paulinho, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Willian \u1edf Brazil \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nWillian s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3, anh c\u0169ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. \u00d4ng Valverde mu\u1ed1n Barca chi \u0111\u1eadm mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m\u00a01988. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Barca \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Willian.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh khi ch\u01b0a quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ai s\u1ebd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi th\u00ec h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Willian n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Willian ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Barca l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi Camp Nou.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willian ghi ban cho Chelsea\" title=\"Willian ghi ban cho Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/willian-chinh-thuc-len-tieng-truoc-tin-don-duoc-barca-quan-tam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Willian l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cBarca l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf \u0111\u00f3. T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t th\u00f4ng tin xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean b\u00e1o ch\u00ed, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o t\u1eeb Barca c\u1ea3. Hi\u1ec7n t\u00f4i \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung cho World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Brazil, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Barca th\u00ec M.U c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Willian, Mourinho r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"900","checkdouble":"190386"},{"date":"06:31 05/07","title":"Sao sa c\u01a1 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea7u c\u1ee9u Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/shaqiri-muon-o-lai-premier-league.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Xherdan Shaqiri mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League thay v\u00ec xu\u1ed1ng gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh c\u00f9ng Stoke City. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y thay cho l\u1eddi nh\u1eafc v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang theo \u0111u\u1ed5i anh nh\u01b0 Liverpool hay Tottenham.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Shaqiri c\u00f9ng Stoke xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, Stoke City ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 19 tr\u00ean BXH Premier League. Sau 38 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, 12 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a trong khi \u0111\u00e3 thua t\u1edbi 19. Qua \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh The Potters ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i xu\u1ed1ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc cho ng\u00f4i sao Xherdan Shaqiri. Chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch 2017/18 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129. Anh \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, 7 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Stoke. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 35 b\u00e0n, t\u00ednh ra Shaqiri \u0111\u00e3 tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o 43% s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Shaqiri mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League thay v\u00ec xu\u1ed1ng gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Shaqiri mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League thay v\u00ec xu\u1ed1ng gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/shaqiri-muon-o-lai-premier-league.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Xherdan Shaqiri mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Xherdan Shaqiri mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 Liverpool hay Tottenham \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft. \u201cT\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec. T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i s\u1ebd s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft\u201d, Shaqiri n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y b\u1edfi t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0110TQG v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 CLB quan t\u00e2m c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. \u0110\u00f4i khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o t\u00f4i. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i \u1edf s\u00e2n kh\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady d\u00f9 trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd bi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Shaqiri c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Th\u1ee5y S\u0129. Anh \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n, 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i b\u1edfi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-muon-gay-soc-voi-chu-lun-de-thuong-172-187932.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/24/liverpool-muon-gay-soc-voi-chu-lun-de-thuong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-muon-gay-soc-voi-chu-lun-de-thuong-172-187932.html\">Liverpool mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi \u201cch\u00fa l\u00f9n\u201d d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span><br>\r\n<span>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Xherdan Shaqiri c\u1ee7a Stoke City \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng bi\u00ean, The Kop s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 12 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"899","checkdouble":"190387"},{"date":"06:37 05/07","title":"Wenger b\u1ecb ch\u00e2m bi\u1ebfm sau ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n s\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 Jordan Pickford","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/wenger-bi-cham-biem-sau-phat-ngon-soc-ve-jordan-pickford.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arsene Wenger ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jordan Pickford, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Everton l\u00e0 m\u1eaft x\u00edch y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Colombia. C\u1ef1u HLV Arsenal \u0111ang g\u1eb7p r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i l\u1edbn v\u1edbi nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsene Wenger ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u s\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 Jordan Pickford</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-colombia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-47-co-den-tay-lieu-co-phat-421-190241.html\" target=\"_blank\">Anh vs Colombia</span>, HLV Arsene Wenger \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh. C\u1ef1u HLV c\u1ee7a Arsenal kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jordan Pickford l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1eaft x\u00edch y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsene Wenger ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jordan Pickford h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Arsene Wenger ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jordan Pickford h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/wenger-bi-cham-biem-sau-phat-ngon-soc-ve-jordan-pickford.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Wenger nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 Jordan Pickford</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cGareth Southgate \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Pickford nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i y\u00ean t\u00e2m, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y 24 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao. T\u00e2m l\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Pickford, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1eaft x\u00edch y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Anh\u201d.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cKhi b\u1ea1n nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup, h\u1ecd lu\u00f4n s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n l\u1edbn, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ker Casillas ho\u1eb7c Manuel Neuer. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o \u0111\u0103ng quang ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cPickford c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t \u1edf Premier League, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u0110TQG. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y qu\u00e1 thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng s\u1ee9c \u00e9p s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Wenger b\u1ecb ch\u00e2m bi\u1ebfm sau d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 Pickford</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsene Wenger ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jordan Pickford, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Everton l\u00e0 m\u1eaft x\u00edch y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Colombia. C\u1ef1u HLV Arsenal \u0111ang g\u1eb7p r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i l\u1edbn v\u1edbi nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jordan Pickford giup Anh vao tu ket World Cup 2018\" title=\"Jordan Pickford gi\u00fap Anh v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/Diem-nhan-Anh-vs-Colombia-vong-18-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jordan Pickford ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc qua \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Wenger b\u1ecb ch\u00e2m bi\u1ebfm</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPickford \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Colombia, ch\u00ednh m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a anh tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m gi\u00fap Tam s\u01b0 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i cho th\u1ea5y anh \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng s\u1ee9c \u00e9p r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u c\u00e2n n\u00e3o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Pickford khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ee7a Wenger bi\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh tr\u00f2 c\u01b0\u1eddi cho NHM, tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Twitter, ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u HLV Arsenal tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec1 t\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n t\u00e1n s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00d4ng Wenger th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n b\u1ecb so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Pele, ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n to\u00e0n sai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd sau v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y \u201cGi\u00e1o s\u01b0\u201d c\u1ea7n c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn h\u01a1n trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"898","checkdouble":"190388"},{"date":"06:52 05/07","title":"Chelsea s\u1eafp c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/23/chelsea-sap-co-tien-dao-tri-gia-53-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea mua Gonzalo Higuain th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, theo Sport Mediaset, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Higuain</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Sarri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1eafp ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Chelsea thay Conte. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi The Blues nh\u01b0ng danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i g\u1eedi l\u00ean BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Chelsea mua Gonzalo Higuain c\u00f3 di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Chelsea mua Gonzalo Higuain c\u00f3 di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/Thuong-vu-Chelsea-mua-Gonzalo-Higuain-co-dien-bien-moi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Higuain\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u HLV Napoli mu\u1ed1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat m\u1edbi tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia nh\u1eafm Gonzalo Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Sarri \u1edf Napoli. M\u00f9a 2015/16, Higuain ghi 36 b\u00e0n \u1edf Serie A d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Sarri.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Higuain v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n Chelsea chi \u0111\u1eadm mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea mua Gonzalo Higuain th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, theo Sport Mediaset, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u\u00a0th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Italia \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Higuain. Juventus \u0111\u00e3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u00e3 31 tu\u1ed5i, kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady anh c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao khi ch\u1ec9 ghi 16 b\u00e0n \u1edf Serie A m\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHiguain hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 sau khi Argentina b\u1ecb Ph\u00e1p lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018. Ngo\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina, Chelsea c\u00f2n nh\u1eafm h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Daniele Rugani c\u0169ng c\u1ee7a Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Morata s\u1eafp ra \u0111i</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Chelsea \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n Gonzalo Higuain, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Morata s\u1ebd b\u1ecb b\u00e1n \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Hi\u1ec7n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/juventus-chi-60-trieu-euro-mua-sao-khung-chelsea-172-185574.html\" target=\"_blank\">Juventus c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Morata</span>, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus muon doi Higuain lay Morata\" title=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Higuain l\u1ea5y Morata\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/juventus-san-sang-trao-doi-bom-tan-voi-chelsea.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Higuain s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u1ed7 Morata</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea v\u00e0 Juventus trao \u0111\u1ed5i gi\u1eefa Morata v\u00e0 Higuain l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng cho c\u00e1c b\u00ean. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Morata c\u0169ng \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 Morata t\u1eebng c\u00f3 2 n\u0103m ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho Juventus theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Real Madrid, b\u1edfi v\u1eady anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Serie A.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"897","checkdouble":"190389"},{"date":"06:53 05/07","title":"Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/granqvist-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-thuy-dien-vs-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Granqvist ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh. Trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0110T Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi HLV Janne Andersson g\u1ecdi l\u1ea1i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u Zlatan Ibrahimovic. R\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng. Nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc \u00c2u v\u1eabn g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng \u00edt h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf 3 trong s\u1ed1 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua c\u1ee7a World Cup, m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 k\u00edn k\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n. H\u1ecd th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 1-0, Mexico 3-0 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 thua \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. T\u1edbi v\u00f2ng 1/8, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 1-0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Granqvist ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Granqvist ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/Granqvist-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-Thuy-Dien-vs-Anh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nS\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111ang gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ngo\u00e0i mong \u0111\u1ee3i. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Toni Kroos v\u00e0o ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c, h\u1ecd th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Andreas Granqvist, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 ghi 2 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m 11m kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn khi \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi Anh. \u201cTh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft l\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng n\u01a1i m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n\u201d, Granqvist ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/granqvist-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-thuy-dien-vs-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Granqvist ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 qua c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh kh\u00e1c. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111i theo con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 21h ng\u00e0y 7/7 t\u1edbi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Samara Arena.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-anh-cap-nhat-tinh-hinh-chan-thuong-cua-vardy-421-190385.html\">\u0110T Anh c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Vardy</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-anh-southgate-va-niem-tin-mu-quang-vao-raheem-sterling-421-190376.html\">\u0110T Anh: Southgate v\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m tin m\u00f9 qu\u00e1ng v\u00e0o Raheem Sterling</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-anh-vs-colombia-vet-seo-dai-qua-khu-nguoi-anh-421-190356.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: V\u1ebft s\u1eb9o d\u00e0i qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch x\u00f3a m\u1edd c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/southgate-dt-anh-khong-the-de-lich-su-ngang-chan-minh-469-190367.html\">Southgate: \u0110T Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed ng\u00e1ng ch\u00e2n m\u00ecnh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lingard-anh-da-cho-doi-ngay-nay-rat-lau-roi-421-190364.html\">Lingard: Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i ng\u00e0y n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u r\u1ed3i</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"896","checkdouble":"190391"}]}